scene.message:
Nanjo: Yamaoka took me to see{nl}
ballet when I was little...{nl}
Meant to cultivate my{nl}
sensibilities, I suppose.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Man, this kind of thing{nl}
throws me off~ Hey, let's get{nl}
to the hospital already!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Ballet, huh...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
"The Nutcracker" is{nl}
a good one.{waitkey}{clearbox}A girl's joyful dream world{nl}
on Christmas night...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
sigh, how lovely...{waitkey}{clearbox}What's with that face?! I{nl}
like ballet, okay?! Problem?!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Pointe shoes are{nl}
surprisingly stiff, you know.{nl}
Didn't know that, did you?{nl}
I was shocked my first time.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Thanks to the gym{nl}
rebuild, we got a club room.{nl}
What a relief.{waitkey}{clearbox}I mean, changing in the{nl}
classroom, someone might{nl}
peep on you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ah! Don't tell me you came{nl}
to peep too?!{waitkey}{ret}
